 Indeed, this was the case (see Figure ??).
 So if land is 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

the economic fulcrum of the capitalist remaking of geography
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
