, one might expect economic geographers not only to have much to say in
 the wake of the crisis about the role of land rent, but also to have been
 intensely studying land rent before the crisis and perhaps even to have
 been among those who predicted it.
 Unfortunately, this was not the case 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "ward2016virtual"

\end_inset

, and this lacunae appears to be yet another 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

